Issues.Body:
I do not see why, but the guard below causes reload of the whole page.
```
canActivate(
    route: ActivatedRouteSnapshot,
    state: RouterStateSnapshot
  ): Observable<boolean> {
    return of(true)
      .pipe(delay(5000))
      .pipe(
        map(response => {
          return response;
        })
      );
  }
```
If I remove the delay the guard works as expected. In the real scenario, I have an API call there. What I do not see? Is it a bug, my mistake?

The optimizations are suggested to;
1) disables ngDevMode via terser
2) helps with cold server starts the same way as client by lowering JS parse times

